Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:02.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.59,0:00:06.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Natsu, don't you think our guild \Nhas a whole lot of special events?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:09.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... There's the that \Nbig parade, the Fantasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:10.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's the hanami bingo tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:13.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't forget about the \NMiss Fairy Tail contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:16.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did you win that, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't ask me that... Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:06.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:09.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that time of year again! \NThis grand event is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:15.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail's traditional All-Wizards \NMandatory Participation 24 Hours Road Race!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:20.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I, Jason, from the Weekly Sorcerer, \Nwill be doing the play-by-play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:25.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be giving you the cool \Nscoop on this hot event!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:30.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,24-Hour Endurance Road Race!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:37.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The unbeatable titleholder \Nfor this road race, Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:42.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors say he's compensating for \Nbeing mostly useless on quests!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:42.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:44.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just rumors, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:48.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Jet... He thinks this year's \Ngonna be a walk in the park again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:51.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? I wouldn't be so sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:57.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody who says "victory is \Nmine" ever actually wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I gots me a super-secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:03.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A secret weapon? You're such a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're drinking? Right \Nbefore we start the run?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't run without fuel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:16.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd say \Nsomething like that, Cana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's really revved up, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:21.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one wants to face the \Npunishment, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:24.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Last year was horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:26.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All members of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:35.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A wizard is one with both \Nstrength of mind and body!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:39.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish for you to utilize those powers \Nto the utmost in today's competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we really need smarts for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:44.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems pretty much just \Nphysical endurance to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:46.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rules are simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will run as fast as you \Ncan from the start line,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:52.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then here along the appointed \Ncourse, heading for Mt. Ivor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:56.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This year, I have left Wyvern \Nscales at the top of Mt. Ivor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:04:02.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will take one of those scales, \Nand return here within 24 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept any dropouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:07.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are a Fairy Tail Wizard, \Nthen you will run the distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,all the way to your next job tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:16.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, I am imposing a new regulation \Nthis year at the urging of many...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flying magic is forbidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than that, any type \Nof magic is allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:25.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one crafty old fox...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:28.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Every year he just goes overboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:31.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, the person who comes in last
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:35.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,will face a punishment of which there \Nis nothing scarier on the planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:41.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this all because the master looks \Nforward to giving out the punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:43.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Last year was just awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only one person, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:48.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't come \Nin last, what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:51.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a quite logical way of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:53.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is far too negative!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:54.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I compete only to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:02.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a special outfit that \Nreduces my muscle fatigue,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:05.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,allowing me to run continuously \Nfor a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:08.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really going for the win...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:11.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy. Today only, we're rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:13.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:15.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This new rule sucks big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... It's finally time for the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:25.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, to the start line!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy, watch my start!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:31.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:33.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He just wants to show you how cool he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:38.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably don't realize, Lu-chan, but I \Ncouldn't watch him at the start if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:44.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:45.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,High Speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:55.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulling away right at the \Nstart is Jet again this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:00.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't see him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:02.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:10.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Check out my secret weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Fists of the Fire Dragon boosters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:16.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet, Natsu! That's totally not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san, Levy-san, if you'll pardon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:21.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, everyone is our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't have to be so polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:27.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the last ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:30.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, who'll be getting the punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:33.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:41.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:42.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:48.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet's already running off by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And behind him, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The idea of using his Fists of the Fire \NDragon as boosters is totally cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:59.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's Erza and Gajeel \Nleading a huge pack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:02.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will it be that makes a break for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:06.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear from our expert \Ncommentator, Mirajane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:08.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet's so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:10.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...we can't film him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pict Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:32.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for \Nlayin' back and paintin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:35.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All's fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:45.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:46.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beast Arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:53.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:59.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is tough work...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:00.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You drink too much, Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You look just as tired as me, Wakaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd gotten this out of shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we even make it to the goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:14.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn from this, and lay off \Nthe booze and tobacco a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Runes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Freed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's booby-trapped the course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you never going to let us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:33.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know he said anything other than flying \Nmagic is allowed, but this goes too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:35.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said you couldn't go free.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:45.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Practice Questions for the Magic \NFour-Wheeler License Exam"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:49.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's "Practice Questions for the Level \N3 Four Elements Sorcerer Qualification"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:51.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Freed, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:57.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To escape from these runes, you must answer \Nall the questions, and get them all correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:03.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If this race purports to test both \Nphysical and mental strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:07.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then this little side game is \Nentertaining as well as fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:10.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel bitter, blame yourselves \Nfor falling into my trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Freed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:15.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blame ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:18.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was {\i1}you{\i0} who activated the runes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:20.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We{\i0} were just caught up in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:21.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:22.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll solve all the problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:25.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do them yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:27.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You meanies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:31.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She is brave for not using magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:35.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Runes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Titania!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:39.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your senses are as perceptive as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:42.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You may have noticed the \Nrune trap, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:48.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking my running rhythm \Nis a serious offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:50.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I have to get my rhythm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:52.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:53.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:58.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After getting past his tricks, \Nshe zings one back at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:10:01.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The race has gotten completely unpredictable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one wants to face the punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:05.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:08.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's movement near the top of Mt. Ivor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:13.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:18.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The pre-race speculation was right on the \Nmoney, as Jet is the first to reach the summit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:22.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He took a Wyvern scale!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:25.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all he has to do is come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:28.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet's speed isn't waning in the slightest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will get there next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:32.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm beat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:35.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go on anymore. I need a little break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu-chan, you have to keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:39.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But my legs won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:42.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy-chan, you go ahead. I'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:43.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My legs hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can make use of?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone good to rely on at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Maiden, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:57.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Virgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:03.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You called, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:05.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry me up to the peak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:07.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And do it on the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:10.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be a breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:12.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I depart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:17.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fall! I'm gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me down, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:27.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What lovely water...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:29.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fatigue is washing right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:43.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia was also scared of this "punishment", so \Nshe didn't help you, and instead went on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:47.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Juvia is tormented by what she did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:53.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until Gray-sama comes to this place, Juvia \Nwill rest herself in this cool water...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that... Juvia-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:11.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the water-user.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:17.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While she was soaking in the water, she must \Nhave changed herself to water by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Juvia around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:23.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:27.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:34.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there, they stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of fuel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was going full-power all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:55.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:01.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I eat that fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 12 hours since the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:13.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon has already \Nrisen over the night sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:17.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the wizards are taking \NWyvern scales one after another
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:20.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and blasting on to the return course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't slack off on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:14.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fists of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:21.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The 24 Hours Endurance Road Race!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:24.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're well into the second half! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:27.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the wizards, with Wyvern scale in hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:33.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,are racing full speed toward \Nthe Magnolia South Gate Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still in the lead is Jet, as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:40.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is Erza, who \Ndoesn't even look winded!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:44.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The next group is Gray, Lucy, and \NGajeel, who are still running strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:46.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:51.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind them is the full pack in pursuit, \Nnot losing focus for an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:53.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will be coming in last?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:56.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will be receiving the \Npunishment this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:58.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't miss a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:03.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bunch of slackers...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:06.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's liven things up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:19.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The race has entered the final stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:24.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The super-high-speed Jet is so fast, \Nwe've completely lost sight of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and the rest are \Ngutsily gaining ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:33.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:36.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has worked hard through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:44.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We had better switch to our seats at South \NGate Park, and get ready to watch the finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:50.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:51.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:55.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:59.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:01.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Should you be sleeping now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:06.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's gone ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:09.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta make up for lost time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:16.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the last spurt toward the goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle for second is heating up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:21.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We can see Magnolia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:23.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:29.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? He wasn't in the lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:35.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Jet behind us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:39.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, then that means we're \Nin contention to win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:43.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet is catching up as fast as he can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:47.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So fast! Passing them in a flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:50.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:54.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:57.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your trump card for the last spurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:00.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:02.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not catching up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's actually really slow for a rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:05.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She must've bought it based \Non the way it looked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:09.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's more about appearances?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:12.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:21.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now in Magnolia, Jet's finally neck and neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:24.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner has been narrowed \Ndown to one of these 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:25.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fists of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:37.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's fists are out of fuel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he out of contention to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:43.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:45.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Never count Natsu out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:48.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's digging deep into \Ntop groove to close in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:50.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:02.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:06.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:18.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a huge crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:21.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, who's that cool cat coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:22.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:24.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:26.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the goal is right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:44.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! You ran well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:45.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:52.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal! Happy is the winner of this \Nyear's 24 Hours Endurance Road Race!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:56.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,History has been made! Nothing \Nwill ever be the same, folks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:19:00.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! Cool! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:03.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:05.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He got us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:07.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:11.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bad ending, I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He woke me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:17.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah well, I'll let him win this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:20.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:21.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:23.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:26.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming in second is Wendy, \Nand third is Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:30.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The top three spots are occupied \Nby these three Fairy Tail pretties!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:34.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:39.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one wants to face the punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:43.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't step on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:47.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:51.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A battalion of wizards all \Ncrossed the goal at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:54.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick thinking Erza also crossed the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:56.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:58.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:00.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:02.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:04.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for you to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:07.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't no joke! High Speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:08.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go-go-go-goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:15.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The 4 of you crossed at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:19.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This year was whacked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:22.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This finish was cooler than cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:27.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming in last was, incredibly, \NNatsu, Gajeel, Gray, and Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:30.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We know who'll get punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:33.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:35.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:38.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps! At least let us have a tie-breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:40.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hear any more \Nof your pitiful excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:48.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For a wizard, there are no \Ndo-overs, for jobs or otherwise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:51.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop acting like babies \Nand take your punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All four of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us what the punishment is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:02.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There! That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:05.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now announce this year's punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:07.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:10.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weekly Sorcerer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:19.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The four of you will do a super-embarrassing \Nphoto spread for the issue two weeks from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:24.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A super-magnificent 20 pages, together \Nwith a one-week, all-access interview!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:29.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A super-embarrassing photo spread?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:34.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go buy a display and \Npreservation tools, Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:35.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:40.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, everyone... Let's go right \Nahead and start picking out clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:45.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:46.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:48.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're running again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.67,0:21:53.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems they still have plenty of stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.18,0:21:55.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:58.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama's photo spread!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:00.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:04.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won, so do I get something nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:06.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You already did!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:12.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You got the joy of winning \Nand everyone's cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:15.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no greater honor, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:17.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:19.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.42,0:22:21.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.45,0:22:23.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:58.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts has finally come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.26,0:24:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! He's been away on a quest \Nfor who knows how many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.74,0:24:04.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to meet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.45,0:24:05.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:07.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When he gets back, I'm \Nchallenging him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.27,0:24:08.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you'll just lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.84,0:24:10.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:11.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely win!
